{"id":47943,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":12,"day":11}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园(第18期)","column":"诗歌","genre":"文学作品","count":"147","ytitle":"","mtitle":"爱","ftitle":"","authors":["李明伦"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱我的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱我国的国旗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是何等的美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随风飘摇在空际。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱我的故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我更爱我的母亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡是多么的使人留恋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲的爱是多么的伟大高深!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱我的弟弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我更爱他那天真的顽皮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是多么的聪明伶俐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未先开口笑嘻嘻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱我们的同胞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我更爱他们的耐苦精神；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情愿在他乡流离，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿做奴隶顺民!"}]}